    <item>
      <title>关税加剧通胀担忧，美国国债收益率下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/treasuries-fall-on-short-end-as-tariffs-deepen-inflation-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对主要贸易伙伴加征关税的举动，加剧了人们对通胀风险的担忧，推高了对利率预期变化最为敏感的短期债券收益率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/treasuries-fall-on-short-end-as-tariffs-deepen-inflation-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 01:14:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税措施导致日本股市暴跌，汽车制造商受创最严重</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/japan-stocks-fall-as-trump-tariffs-stoke-fears-of-trade-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普宣布对美国三大贸易伙伴加征关税，威胁将对经济造成重大破坏，日本股市暴跌，日经指数一度下跌近 3%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/japan-stocks-fall-as-trump-tariffs-stoke-fears-of-trade-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 00:17:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
